    "body": [
      "# AI Agent Snippet Help",
      "",
      "## Available Snippets:",
      "1. api-feature        — New API feature (domain + data, no presentation)",
      "2. api-feature-extend — Add a method to an existing feature",
      "3. cubit-form         — Form cubit: standalone Freezed state + FormInput validation + buildParams()",
      "4. cubit-fetch        — Fetch/operation cubit: sealed union Freezed state (part file pattern)",
      "5. full-feature       — Complete feature: domain + data + presentation layers",
      "6. screen-route       — Screen + GoRoute + body/form widget only",
      "",
      "## Key Project Rules (enforced in all snippets):",
      "",
      "### Endpoint",
      "- Always add new endpoint to lib/core/network/api_endpoints.dart",
      "- Static: static const methodName = '/path/to/endpoint';",
      "- Dynamic: static String methodName(String id) => '/path/$id';",
      "",
      "### Params",
      "- Location: feature/domain/params/xxx_params.dart",
      "- Barrel:   domain/params/params.dart",
      "- Pattern:  extends Params, Equatable props, pure Dart",
      "- Skip if usecase uses NoParams (no inputs needed)",
      "",
      "### Barrel Files",
      "- domain/params/params.dart          — all params",
      "- domain/usecases/usecases.dart      — all usecases + re-export params",
      "- domain/entities/entities.dart      — all entities",
      "- data/models/models.dart            — all model sub-barrels",
      "- data/models/xxx/xxx.dart           — per-model sub-barrel",
      "",
      "### Request Models (POST/PUT/PATCH)",
      "- @JsonSerializable(createFactory: false)  ← NO fromJson",
      "- factory XxxRequestModel.fromParams(XxxParams params)",
      "- toJson() only",
      "",
      "### Response Models",
      "- @JsonSerializable(createToJson: false)  ← NO toJson",
      "- fromJson + toEntity getter",
      "- List responses: source uses response.parseList(Model.fromJson)",
      "",
      "### Data Source Impl",
      "- @Injectable(as: XxxRemoteSource)  ← typed annotation",
      "- Constructor: @Named(InjectionNames.apiClientAuth) required this.apiClient",
      "- Response: return response.parse(XxxResponseModel.fromJson);",
      "",
      "### Repository Impl",
      "- @LazySingleton(as: XxxRepository) extends BaseRepository implements XxxRepository",
      "- Constructor: required super.networkInfo",
      "- ALWAYS use handleException(() async { ... }, operationName: 'methodName')",
      "- Return: (await _remote.xxx(...)).data.toEntity",
      "- NEVER throw raw exceptions",
      "",
      "### DI",
      "- Remote source impl: @Injectable(as: XxxRemoteSource)",
      "- Local source impl:  @LazySingleton(as: XxxLocalSource)",
      "- Repository impl:    @LazySingleton(as: XxxRepository)",
      "- UseCase:            @injectable",
      "- Feature cubit:      @injectable  (provided per-screen via BlocProvider in route)",
      "- Global cubit:       @lazySingleton  (added to global_app_providers.dart)",
      "",
      "### Freezed States — TWO patterns",
      "FORM STATE (standalone file):",
      "- File: xxx_form_state.dart with own part 'xxx_form_state.freezed.dart'",
      "- Must be: @freezed abstract class (not class) when using ._() for custom getters",
      "- Fields: @Default(FormInput.pure('')) FormInput<String> fieldName",
      "- Touch-gated error: String? get err => field.errorFrom(AppValidators.xxx.call)",
      "- Touch-blind valid: bool get isValid => AppValidators.xxx(field.value) == null",
      "- Cubit: super(XxxFormState.initial())  ← NO const; imports state file normally",
      "",
      "FETCH/OP STATE (part file):",
      "- File: xxx_state.dart  with 'part of xxx_cubit.dart' as first line",
      "- Regular class (not abstract), sealed union: initial/loading/success/error",
      "- Error variant: error(Failure failure) = _Error  ← NEVER _Failure",
      "- Cubit: part 'xxx_cubit.freezed.dart' BEFORE part 'xxx_state.dart'",
      "- Cubit: super(const XxxState.initial())  ← const OK on sealed union variants",
      "- freezed_annotation import lives in CUBIT file, inherited by state via 'part of'",
      "",
      "- NEVER use Equatable for cubit states",
      "",
      "### Route Pattern",
      "- Route class extends GoRoute",
      "- Provides cubits: BlocProvider(create: (_) => getIt<XxxCubit>())",
      "- Multiple cubits: MultiBlocProvider(providers: [...])",
      "- Auto-fetch on open: getIt<XxxCubit>()..fetch()",
      "- Screen always has const constructor; no cubit passed via constructor",
      "",
      "### Screen Pattern",
      "- StatelessWidget with const constructor",
      "- BlocListener for side-effects (snackbars, navigation)",
      "- BlocBuilder in body widget (not directly in screen)",
      "- Form screens wrap Scaffold in KeyboardDismissible",
      "",
      "### Body / Form Widgets",
      "- Body (display):  StatelessWidget — reads state via BlocBuilder",
      "- Form (edit):     StatefulWidget — has TextEditingControllers, initState, dispose",
      "  - initState: read cubits, init controllers, call formCubit.initializeForm(data)",
      "  - _handleSubmit: call formCubit.buildParams() → if not null → call opCubit.execute()",
      "",
      "### Logging",
      "- Import: package:niramoy_health_app/core/app/logger/console_app_logger.dart",
      "- Use: logger.d() / logger.i() / logger.w() / logger.e()",
      "- Failure has: failure.title (heading) + failure.details (full message)",
      "- NEVER use print() or dart:developer log()",
      "",
      "### Navigation",
      "- context.push(RouteNames.xxx)  — push (back button available)",
      "- context.go(RouteNames.xxx)    — replace current location",
      "- context.pop()                 — go back",
      "",
      "## Usage:",
      "1. Open a Markdown or Plaintext file",
      "2. Type snippet prefix → Tab to expand → Tab through placeholders",
      "3. Copy filled prompt into Claude Code",
      "",
      "After any annotated change: fvm dart run build_runner build --delete-conflicting-outputs",
      "",
      "Full template reference: see .claude/skills/*.md"
    ],
    "description": "Show help for all AI agent prompt snippets"
